item.title: CVE-2021-21444|2024-08-03T18:16:22.235Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20business%20objects%20business%20intelligence%20platform%20%28cmc%20and%20bi%20launchpad%29
item.description: SAP Business Objects BI Platform, versions - 410, 420, 430, allows multiple X-Frame-Options headers entries in the response headers, which may not be predictably treated by all user agents. This could, as a result, nullify the added X-Frame-Options header leading to Clickjacking attack.
